&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; nallavan ( english : good man for good man ) is a tamil film , directed by sp . muthuraman . the film was a remake of 1983 telugu film &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; starring krishnam raju and jayasudha . the film was later remade in kannada as jeevana chakra ( 1985 ) starring vishnuvardhan and raadhika sarathkumar in main roles . it was a blockbuster and completed a &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; run at the box office .